caption: It was so neat! We wish we could have stayed longer. If you are staying in one of the hotels around they may have a code. Decent enough place and cool building, but the drinks are far better at The Patterson House. It wasn’t bad though, just not as good as I thought it would be. Definitely sticking to the Pat. House for my cocktails, but if you have cigar loving friends, this place does that well.
